    <item>
      <title>特朗普贬值美元的承诺可能为比特币带来利好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/trump-s-weaker-dollar-pledge-plots-possible-tailwind-for-bitcoin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果前美国总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的计划得逞，他可能于 11 月重返白宫，这可能导致美元贬值。一些分析师认为，这将有利于比特币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/trump-s-weaker-dollar-pledge-plots-possible-tailwind-for-bitcoin</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 16:12:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行任命布伦纳为 TMT 投资银行主管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/bank-of-america-names-brunner-as-head-of-tmt-investment-banking</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻社看到的一份内部备忘录显示，美国银行公司已任命凯文·布伦纳 (Kevin Brunner) 为全球科技、媒体和电信投资银行业务主管。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/bank-of-america-names-brunner-as-head-of-tmt-investment-banking</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 16:02:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行考虑将杠杆贷款调查需求减半至 70 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/ecb-weighs-halving-demand-in-leverage-loan-probe-to-7-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行官员正在讨论要求银行增加约 70 亿欧元（76 亿美元）的杠杆贷款坏账拨备，约为最初估计的一半，此前该行对该业务的深入审查引发了银行的强烈反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/ecb-weighs-halving-demand-in-leverage-loan-probe-to-7-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 16:02:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DeFi 交易所 DYdX 正在洽谈出售衍生品交易平台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/defi-exchange-dydx-said-to-be-in-talks-to-sell-derivatives-trading-platform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，同名去中心化金融交易所的开发商 DYdX Trading Inc. 正在洽谈将其部分衍生品交易软件出售给一个包括一些加密货币最大做市商在内的财团，具体金额未公开。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/defi-exchange-dydx-said-to-be-in-talks-to-sell-derivatives-trading-platform</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 15:51:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
